JOHANNESBURG Umkhonto We Sizwe veterans and ANC supporters have gathered outside Luthuli House to defend the ANC headquarters amid mass action by civil society calling on President Jacob Zuma to step down.ANC supporters also gathered at Beyers Naud Square next to Luthuli House to show support for the ruling party and President Zuma.Protests across the country by civil society organisations are calling on the President to step down.eNCA